<p><strong>The Popular Encyclopedia of Apologetics Surveying the Evidence</strong></p>
<p>The Popular Encyclopedia of Apologetics Surveying the Evidence is a comprehensive resource for Christians who want to defend their faith. It covers a wide range of topics, from the existence of God to the reliability of the Bible. This article will answer some questions about the book and its contents.</p>
